{"name":"gpinyin","description":"gpinyin - use\nHanyu Pinyin Chinese in roff","body":"\n\n<h1 align=\"center\">GPINYIN</h1>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<hr>\n\n\n<h2>NAME\n<a name=\"NAME\"></a>\n</h2>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">gpinyin - use\nHanyu Pinyin Chinese in roff</p>\n\n<h2>SYNOPSIS\n<a name=\"SYNOPSIS\"></a>\n</h2>\n\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" rules=\"none\" frame=\"void\"\n       cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"11%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\"><b>gpinyin</b></p></td>\n<td width=\"1%\"></td>\n<td width=\"25%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\">[<i>input-file</i> ...]</p></td>\n<td width=\"52%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"11%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\"><b>gpinyin</b></p></td>\n<td width=\"1%\"></td>\n<td width=\"25%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\"><b>-h</b></p></td>\n<td width=\"52%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"11%\">\n\n\n<p><b>gpinyin</b></p></td>\n<td width=\"1%\"></td>\n<td width=\"25%\">\n\n\n<p><b>--help</b></p></td>\n<td width=\"52%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"11%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\"><b>gpinyin</b></p></td>\n<td width=\"1%\"></td>\n<td width=\"25%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\"><b>-v</b></p></td>\n<td width=\"52%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"11%\">\n\n\n<p><b>gpinyin</b></p></td>\n<td width=\"1%\"></td>\n<td width=\"25%\">\n\n\n<p><b>--version</b></p></td>\n<td width=\"52%\">\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>DESCRIPTION\n<a name=\"DESCRIPTION\"></a>\n</h2>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>gpinyin</b>\nis a preprocessor for <a href=\"https://man.page/1/groff\">groff(1)</a> that facilitates use\nof the Hanyu Pinyin <a href=\"https://man.page/7/groff\">groff(7)</a> files. Pinyin is a\nmethod for writing the Chinese language with the Latin\nalphabet. The Chinese language consists of more than four\nhundred syllables, each with one of five different tones. In\nPinyin, a syllable is written in the Latin alphabet and a\nnumeric tone indicator can be appended to each syllable.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">Each\n<i>input-file</i> is a file name or the hyphen-minus\ncharacter &ldquo;-&rdquo; to indicate that standard input\nshould be read. As usual, the argument &ldquo;--&rdquo; can\nbe used in order to force interpretation of all remaining\narguments as file names, even if an <i>input-file</i>\nargument begins with the hyphen-minus character.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>Pinyin\nSections</b> <br>\nPinyin sections in <i>groff</i> files are enclosed by two\n<b>.pinyin</b> requests with different arguments. The\nstarting request is</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:22%;\">.pinyin start</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%;\">or</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:22%;\">.pinyin begin</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%;\">and the ending request is</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:22%;\">.pinyin stop</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%;\">or</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:22%;\">.pinyin end</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%;\">.</p>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>Syllables</b>\n<br>\nThe spoken Chinese language is based on about 411\n<i>syllables</i>; see\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pinyin_table\">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pinyin_table</a>.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">In Pinyin, each\nsyllable consists of one to six letters from the Latin\nalphabet; these letters comprise the fifty-two upper- and\nlowercase letters from the ASCII character set, plus the\nletter &ldquo;U&rdquo; with dieresis (umlaut) in both\ncases&mdash;in other words, the members of the set\n&ldquo;[a&ndash;zA&ndash;Z&uuml;&Uuml;]&rdquo;.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">In <i>groff</i>\ninput, all ASCII letters are written as themselves. The\n&ldquo;u with dieresis&rdquo; can be written as\n&ldquo;\\[:u]&rdquo; in lowercase or &ldquo;\\[:U]&rdquo; in\nuppercase. Within <b>.pinyin</b> sections, <i>gpinyin</i>\nsupports the form &ldquo;ue&rdquo; for lowercase and the\nforms &ldquo;Ue&rdquo; and &ldquo;UE&rdquo; for\nuppercase.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>Tones</b>\n<br>\nEach syllable has exactly one of five <i>tones</i>. The\nfifth tone is not explicitly written at all, but each of the\nfirst through fourth tones is indicated with a diacritic\nabove a specific vowel within the syllable.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">In a\n<i>gpinyin</i> source file, these tones are written by\nadding a numeral in the range 0 to 5 after the syllable. The\ntone numbers 1 to 4 are transformed into accents above\nvowels in the output. The tone numbers 0 and 5 are\nsynonymous.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">The following\ntable summarizes the tones. Some output devices will not be\nable to render every output example.</p>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" rules=\"none\" frame=\"void\"\n       cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"23%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"7%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"23%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"23%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"23%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"23%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"23%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"23%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"23%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"7%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"7%\"></td>\n<td width=\"8%\"></td>\n<td width=\"23%\">\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"grohtml-1482291.png\" alt=\"Image grohtml-1482291.png\"></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">The neutral\ntone number can be omitted from a word-final syllable, but\nnot otherwise.</p>\n\n<h2>OPTIONS\n<a name=\"OPTIONS\"></a>\n</h2>\n\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" rules=\"none\" frame=\"void\"\n       cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"9%\">\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 1em\"><b>-h</b></p></td>\n<td width=\"2%\"></td>\n<td width=\"50%\">\n</td>\n<td width=\"28%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"9%\">\n\n\n<p><b>--help</b></p></td>\n<td width=\"2%\"></td>\n<td width=\"50%\">\n\n\n<p>Print usage information and exit.</p></td>\n<td width=\"28%\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr valign=\"top\" align=\"left\">\n<td width=\"11%\"></td>\n<td width=\"9%\">\n\n\n<p><b>-v</b></p></td>\n<td width=\"2%\"></td>\n<td width=\"50%\"></td>\n<td width=\"28%\">\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%;\"><b>--version</b></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:22%;\">Print version information and\nexit.</p>\n\n<h2>AUTHORS\n<a name=\"AUTHORS\"></a>\n</h2>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><b>gpinyin</b>\nwas written by\n<a href=\"mailto:<groff-bernd.warken-72@web.de>\">Bernd\nWarken</a>.</p>\n\n<h2>SEE ALSO\n<a name=\"SEE ALSO\"></a>\n</h2>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\">Useful\ndocuments on the World Wide Web related to Pinyin\ninclude</p>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:17%;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pinyin\">&ldquo;Pinyin&rdquo;\n(Wikipedia)</a>, <br>\n\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pinyin_table\">&ldquo;Pinyin\ntable&rdquo; (Wikipedia)</a>, <br>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.foolsworkshop.com/ptou/index.html\"><i>Pinyin\nto Unicode</i></a>, <br>\n<a href=\"http://www.mandarintools.com/\"><i>On-line Chinese\nTools</i></a>, <br>\n<a href=\"http://www.pinyin.info/index.html\"><i>Pinyin.info:\na guide to the writing of Mandarin Chinese in roman-\nization</i></a>, <br>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.pinyin.info/rules/where.html\">&ldquo;Where\ndo the tone marks go?&rdquo; (Pinyin.info)</a>, <br>\n\n<a href=\"http://git.savannah.gnu.org/gitweb/?p=cjk.git;a=blob_plain;f=doc/pinyin.txt;hb=HEAD\">pinyin.txt\nfrom the CJK macro package for TeX</a>,</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%;\">and</p>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:17%;\"><a href=\"http://git.savannah.gnu.org/gitweb/?p=cjk.git;a=blob_plain;f=texinput/pinyin.sty;hb=HEAD\">pinyin.sty\nfrom the CJK macro package for TeX</a>.</p>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><a href=\"https://man.page/1/groff\">groff(1)</a>,\n<a href=\"https://man.page/1/grog\">grog(1)</a>, and <a href=\"https://man.page/1/groffer\">groffer(1)</a> explain how to view\n<i>roff</i> documents.</p>\n\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:11%; margin-top: 1em\"><a href=\"https://man.page/7/groff\">groff(7)</a>\nand <a href=\"https://man.page/7/groff_char\">groff_char(7)</a> are comprehensive references\ncovering the language elements of GNU <i>roff</i> and the\navailable glyph repertoire, respectively.</p>\n<hr>\n","headings":["<a href=\"#NAME\">NAME</a>","<a href=\"#SYNOPSIS\">SYNOPSIS</a>","<a href=\"#DESCRIPTION\">DESCRIPTION</a>","<a href=\"#OPTIONS\">OPTIONS</a>","<a href=\"#AUTHORS\">AUTHORS</a>","<a href=\"#SEE ALSO\">SEE ALSO</a>"]}